The paper proposes a new algorithm for many-objective combinatorial optimization problems. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) which deals with optimization problems, Machine Learning (cs.LG) which often involves optimization, Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) which deals with combinatorial optimization, Robotics (cs.RO) which often involves optimization in path planning, and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) which deals with optimization using evolutionary algorithms.
